---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import SuperYesAside from "../../../components/bluey/SuperYesAside.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="SuperYes — Stakeholder Perspectives"
    description="Bluey habitat: cross-functional perspective grid."
    system="bluey"
    chrome="hidden"
>
    <div class="bly-shell">
        <SuperYesAside active="perspectives" verticalText="PERSPECTIVES / Q3-2026" />

        <main class="bly-main">
            <div class="bly-blob bly-blob--white" style="top:-100px; right:-100px; width:600px; height:600px;" aria-hidden="true"></div>

            <header class="bly-header-row">
                <div class="bly-workflow-title">
                    <div class="bly-active-problem">
                        <span class="bly-pulse"></span>
                        Active Problem: Enterprise Checkout Drop-off
                    </div>
                    <h1>Stakeholder Perspectives</h1>
                </div>
            </header>

            <div class="bly-perspective-grid">
                <div class="bly-perspective-col">
                    <div class="bly-column-header">
                        <span class="bly-mono-label">Function</span>
                        <h2>Engineering</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bly-card bly-card--strong bly-viewpoint">
                        <p>"The current validation logic for enterprise tax IDs is synchronous and times out on 3G connections, causing 'ghost' form submissions."</p>
                        <span class="bly-mono-label" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Supporting Evidence</span>
                        <div class="bly-evidence">
                            <div class="bly-evidence-icon" style="background: #F4F0FF; color: #7B61FF;">GH</div>
                            <div class="bly-evidence-text">Issue #1082: Validation Timeout</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bly-evidence">
                            <div class="bly-evidence-icon" style="background: #FFF4F2; color: #FF3F14;">Sn</div>
                            <div class="bly-evidence-text">504 Gateway Timeout +14%</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bly-perspective-col">
                    <div class="bly-column-header">
                        <span class="bly-mono-label">Function</span>
                        <h2>Product</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bly-card bly-card--strong bly-viewpoint">
                        <p>"We're asking for 6 optional fields before the credit card entry. It increases cognitive load and friction for the primary conversion goal."</p>
                        <span class="bly-mono-label" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Supporting Evidence</span>
                        <div class="bly-evidence">
                            <div class="bly-evidence-icon" style="background: #F0F7FF; color: #007AFF;">Mx</div>
                            <div class="bly-evidence-text">Funnel: Step 3 Drop-off</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bly-evidence">
                            <div class="bly-evidence-icon" style="background: #F4F0FF; color: #7B61FF;">Hj</div>
                            <div class="bly-evidence-text">Rage Click Map</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bly-perspective-col">
                    <div class="bly-column-header">
                        <span class="bly-mono-label">Function</span>
                        <h2>Customer Success</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bly-card bly-card--strong bly-viewpoint">
                        <p>"Large accounts complain that they can't save progress. If they miss one field, the whole form clears on mobile refresh."</p>
                        <span class="bly-mono-label" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Supporting Evidence</span>
                        <div class="bly-evidence">
                            <div class="bly-evidence-icon" style="background: #F0F7FF; color: #007AFF;">In</div>
                            <div class="bly-evidence-text">Ticket: 'Lost progress'</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bly-evidence">
                            <div class="bly-evidence-icon" style="background: #FFF4F2; color: #FF3F14;">CS</div>
                            <div class="bly-evidence-text">Q3 Churn Risk: Enterprise</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <footer class="perspective-footer">
                <p>
                    Cross-functional alignment score is <strong>High (84%)</strong>.
                    All perspectives point toward technical friction in the middle-funnel.
                </p>
                <button class="bly-btn bly-btn--primary bly-btn--md">Synthesize Solution</button>
            </footer>
        </main>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .perspective-footer {
        margin-top: 4rem;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        padding-top: 2rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .perspective-footer p {
        opacity: 0.65;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: 0;
    }
</style>

<script>
    if (typeof window !== "undefined") {
        (window as any).wardrobeTrack?.("wardrobe_demo_view", {
            system: "bluey",
            page: "perspectives",
        });
    }
</script>
